                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090215-26-off143 t18090215-26-cd144"></join>, a silk handkerchief, value 5 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18090215-26-victim279" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Robinson
                        <interp inst="t18090215-26-victim279" type="surname" value="Robinson"></interp>
